-IT/wordpress-meetup-terni/events/297758140/\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Lecce</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>ven 15 dic, ore 18:00 “Il simbolo nella comunicazione di brand” –&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/wordpress-meetup-lecce/events/297520975/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Verona</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>lun 18 dic, ore 19:00 “WordCamp Verona e novità 2024” – <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/verona-wordpress-meetup/events/297901535/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Roma</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>mer 20 dic, ore 18:00 “Come realizzare un sito multilingua: i migliori plugin” –&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/romawordpress/events/297790696/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Avezzano</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>ven 22 dic, ore 17:45 “Meetup natalizio” –&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/avezzano-wordpress-meetup/events/297794832/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-dark-blueberry-color has-blueberry-3-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color has-extra-large-font-size wp-elements-21579f84b2404064551679baa70dac93\">&#8230; articolo in aggiornamento&#8230;</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:75:\"https://it.wordpress.org/news/2023/12/tutti-i-meetup-di-dicembre-2023/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"da